T16TD4447E:383b-0: @383b * // lta ba yang dag sgron ma bzhugs //
T16TD4447E:383b-2: # // dpal ldan thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nyi ma'i 'od stong gis //
T16TD4447E:383b-3: shin tu 'bar ba'i zer tsam bdag blo mun par byung //
T16TD4447E:383b-4: dbyangs dang tshig 'das nam mkha'i mtshan nyid las 'das pa'i //
T16TD4447E:383b-5: rang sems skye med zab mo'i don gyi phyogs tsam snang //
T16TD4447E:383b-6: rang gis rtogs pas mkhas pas gsungs pa'i rnam mang ba //
T16TD4447E:383b-7: rtog ge bdag 'dra'i spyod yul rtsom par mi 'os kyang //
T16TD4447E:383b-8: rig pa'i brjed byang tsam 'di nges don mos rnams kyis //
T16TD4447E:383b-9: chos phyir 'brang ba'i blo yis dpyad cing goms par bya //
T16TD4447E:383b-10: bskal pa mang por rgyal ba rnams la ni //
T16TD4447E:383b-11: dge rtsa bskyed cing rang sems sbyangs pa yis //
T16TD4447E:383b-12: rnal 'byor dam pa nges pa'i lung chen la //
T16TD4447E:383b-13: shes rab mchog ldan rig pa'i mos blo gsal //
T16TD4447E:383b-14: rnam par mi rtog don dam rang bzhin gyi //
T16TD4447E:383b-15: rig pa'i tshul chen sems kyis dmigs pa ni //
T16TD4447E:383b-16: lung dang man ngag rigs pas thag bcad de //
T16TD4447E:384a-0: chos kyi rang bzhin yang dag yid @384a * //
T16TD4447E:384a-2: ji ltar nam mkha' la ni tha snyad du //
T16TD4447E:384a-3: ming dang tshig gis rjod par byed mod kyi //
T16TD4447E:384a-4: mtshan ma med cing spros dang bral ba ste //
T16TD4447E:384a-5: ngo bo nyid kyis sems kyi yul las 'das //
T16TD4447E:384a-6: ji ltar smig rgyu'i phung po snang ba dag / snang ba nyid na nam mkha'i rang bzhin ltar ;
T16TD4447E:384a-7: / de bzhin chos rnams sna tshogs ltar snang yang //
T16TD4447E:384a-8: snang ba nyid na mtshan ma nam mkha' bzhin //
T16TD4447E:384a-9: rgya che rab zab theg mchog yangs pa'i lam //
T16TD4447E:384a-10: don dam dmigs med spros pa kun las 'das //
T16TD4447E:384a-11: bdag dang chos kyi dbyings su mnyam pa yi //
T16TD4447E:384a-12: dbu ma'i don can blo yi rting du go bar byos//
T16TD4447E:384a-13: yang dag don dam cig car go nas ni //
T16TD4447E:384a-14: yod med la sogs sems kyi yul 'das shing //
T16TD4447E:384a-15: re dang dogs pa'i mtha' ni rab spangs nas //
T16TD4447E:384a-16: rtsol ba med pa'i brtson 'grus brtsam par bya //
T16TD4447E:384a-17: chos rnams thams cad ye nas ro gcig phyir //
T16TD4447E:384a-18: bsgom pa dang ni bsgom bya'ang dmigs su med//
T16TD4447E:384a-19: sems nyid ye nas chos nyid yin shes na //
T16TD4447E:384a-20: chos kyi dbyings nyid gzhan du bsgom mi dgos //
T16TD4447E:384a-21: rmi lam dag gi bde dang sdug bsngal dag / sad par gyur na rang bzhin mnyam pa ltar //
T16TD4447E:384a-22: rnam par rtog dang mi rtog gnyis ka yang //
T16TD4447E:384a-23: shes pas rig na rang bzhin yongs kyis mnyam //
T16TD4447E:384a-24: de ltar dus gsum rnam par dag pa dag / rang bzhin nyid las ma 'das shes na ni //
T16TD4447E:384a-25: sgro 'dogs bus pa'i rjes su ma 'brangs na //
T16TD4447E:384a-26: rang bzhin ngang du yong gis bcos mi dgos //
T16TD4447E:384a-27: ji ltar nam mkha' mtshan ma med pa'i phyir //
T16TD4447E:384a-28: nam mkha' de nyid bsgom par mi 'gyur bzhin //
T16TD4447E:384a-29: ngo bo nyid kyis ma skyes sems kyis ni //
T16TD4447E:384a-30: ma skyes de nyid bsgom par ga la 'gyur //
T16TD4447E:384a-31: mi mthun pa dang gnyan po dbyer med don //
T16TD4447E:384a-32: rang gis shes na rtsol ba kun spangs te //
T16TD4447E:384a-33: btang snyoms chen por ma bcos ngang bzhag na //
T16TD4447E:384a-34: tha snyad tsam du'ang bsgom zhes de la bya //
T16TD4447E:384a-35: skyon dang yon tan gnyis po ma skyes phyir //
T16TD4447E:384a-36: rnam par rtog pa'i mtshan ma ci byung yang //
T16TD4447E:384a-37: ma bkag rang byung ma 'brangs rang zhi ste //
T16TD4447E:384a-38: ma bcos ma byas rang gi ngang gis gsal //
T16TD4447E:384a-39: lta ba yang dag sgron ma rdzogs so /
T16TD4447E:384a-41: // / a'a tsarya dpal dbyangs kyis mdzad pa'o /
